text: Loures () is a city in the central Portuguese Grande Lisboa Subregion. It is 13 km to the north of Lisbon. It was created on 26 July 1886. The population in 2011 was 199,494,Instituto Nacional de Estatística (INE), Census 2011 results according to the 2013 administrative division of Portugal in an area of 167.24 km². ==References== Category:Cities in Portugal Category:Municipalities of Portugal Category:Lisbon District
title: Loures
